HR Excellence in Research

   HR Execllence in Research In 2008, NTNU was among the first universities in Europe to sign the "European Charter for Researchers" (Charter) and the "European Code of Conduct for the Recruitment
   of Researchers" (Code). Read more about the Charter and Code.

