Fall 2012 programmes

   Learn about Norwegian culture, or come join staff and other international researchers at a monthly get-together -- all sponsored by NTNU's International Researcher Support. Click on the links
   below to download a programme or register for a course.
     * Language cafe -- monthly get-togethers on Monday from 1330 to 1500 with coffee and a Norwegian instructor
     * International coffee -- relax on a Friday from 1100 to 1300 with fellow international researchers and their families. Especially designed for new researchers, held once a month. Click on
       the link to reserve a place.
     * New in Norway -- an introduction to Norwegian culture
     * Autumn 2012 programme -- download the pdf


Learn Norwegian

   Want to get a jump start on learning Norwegian? NTNU's Department of Language and Communication Studies has developed Norwegian on the Web (NoW), an Internet-based all-in-one beginner Norwegian
   course.
